data.name: Presperse
data.description:
For more than 40 years, Presperse has been the trusted partner to the world’s best beauty brands for transformational ingredients, breakthrough formula innovation, and supply- chain excellence. As a recognized leader in quality, sustainability, research, green chemistry, and Corporate Social Responsibility, Presperse provides 400+ premium specialty ingredients and visionary expertise to formulators of skincare, sun care, hair care, color cosmetics, and diverse areas of beauty and wellness. Presperse is recognized as EcoVadis™ Gold, Roundtable for Sustainable Palm Oil, Responsible Mica Initiative, ISO 9001 certified, a signatory on the UN Global Compact, and a certified USA Great Place To Work®.

As a subsidiary of Sumitomo Corporation, Presperse offers clients the global benefits of one of the world’s leading integrated trading firms with financial prowess across trade, distribution, research, regulatory, and diversified industrial and consumer goods.

Let’s make beauty together.™

data.name: BioGenic MagicBead
data.description:
BioGenic MagicBead 100 Series uses a specialized coating technology to create a
single layered non-breakable bead that can be used as a plastic-free scrub
alternative. BioGenic MagicBead 200 Series uses a specialized coating technology to create a
multi-layered, encapsulated, breakable bead that contains oil-soluble active
ingredients

data.name: SiClone
data.description: SiClone® SR-5, a D-5 replacement, has good volatility, slip, cushion, and overall esthetics. It is a volatile silicone replacement comprised of a blend of hydrocarbons.

data.name: Pellicer
data.description:
Pellicer® is a peptide-like, plant-derived, multifunctional active ingredient. It has
excellent surface-active properties and functions in emulsification and dispersion at
very low use levels. Pellicer® does not require heating and can be used in a cold process.
Its ceramide-like gemini structure also gives it a high affinity to skin and hair, providing
moisturizing and damage repair properties.

data.name: BioGenic Gentinol
data.description: Biogenic Gentinol-200 is an encapsulated Retinol (Vitamin A) for cosmetic application. It helps to minimize the appearance of wrinkles by slowing down the breakdown of collagen. Using Multi Stabilizing Technology, Retinol is stabilized and soluble in various applications. Using Gentinol-200 will allow formulation flexibility.

data.name: Sympholight
data.description:
Sympholight “TE” Series has superior water-dispersibility and chemical stability,
resulting in more homogeneous finished products. It has applications in cosmetics and
personal care such as liquid foundation, mascara, eye liner, and skincare emulsions.
These pigments are compatible with carbomers. Sympholight “O” Series has high oil dispersibility and provides uniformity in color,
resulting in a beautiful finish. Since these pigments do not require a high shear process,
manufacturing time and resources may be reduced.

data.name: SiClone® SR-5
data.description: SiClone® SR-5, a D-5 replacement, has good volatility, slip, cushion, and overall esthetics. It is a volatile silicone replacement comprised of a blend of hydrocarbons.

data.name: Permethyl® 101A
data.description: Permethyl® 101A is highly emollient, easy-spreading, and moisturizing. It imparts a non-drying feeling on the skin and has a light, smooth feel with excellent cleansing properties. The Permethyl® line is a series of unique, highly branched aliphatic hydrocarbons ranging from highly volatile, low viscosity liquids to non-volatile viscous materials. The low viscosity grades have excellent makeup removal properties and are differentiated by skin feel, spreadability and volatility. The high viscosity grades give high gloss and film forming properties, and are differentiated by product viscosity.

data.name: Permethyl® 99A
data.description: Permethyl® 99A is highly volatile. It provides a light, non-oily feel with little residue and excellent solvency. The Permethyl® line is a series of unique, highly branched aliphatic hydrocarbons ranging from highly volatile, low viscosity liquids to non-volatile viscous materials. The low viscosity grades have excellent makeup removal properties and are differentiated by skin feel, spreadability and volatility. The high viscosity grades give high gloss and film forming properties, and are differentiated by product viscosity.

data.name: Ganzpearl® GMP-0820
data.description: Ganzpearl® GMP-0820 is a “macroporous” spherical powder characterized by a smooth creamy feel that provides high oil absorbency, soft focus/optical blurring, and SPF boosting capability. It also has good heat & solvent resistance. Average particle size: 8µm

data.name: Pellicer® LB-10
data.description: Pellicer® emulsifiers are a series of plant derived Gemini surfactants consisting of two hydrophobic groups attached to two hydrophilic groups, bonded together by a hydrophilic spacer. This structure provides many excellent emulsification and dispersion properties. Composed of naturally derived fatty acids and peptides, it also aids in hair penetration and adhesion. It also aids in skin penetration and damage repair.

data.name: BioGenic Sallic-210
data.description: BioGenic Sallic-210 is a cosmetic grade material. It is a highly-concentrated (40%) water-soluble salicylic acid allows for up to 10% of salicylic acid to be soluble in water without recrystallization or skin irritation.

data.name: Silica Baloon BA-4
data.description: Silica Balloon BA-4 is a micro-balloon silica bead with a light, soft texture. Its non-porous surface does not exhibit dullness, making the skin appear brighter while having SPF Boosting efficacy. Oil absorption 40 mL/100-gram powder. Average particle size: 4µm.

data.name: BioGenic Caffeine 210
data.description: BioGenic Caffeine-210 enables the use of high concentrations of caffeine in aqueous formulations without exhibiting recrystallization. It provides anticellulite and anti-dark circle effects.

data.name: Pellicer® L-30
data.description: Pellicer® emulsifiers are a series of plant derived Gemini surfactants consisting of two hydrophobic groups attached to two hydrophilic groups, bonded together by a hydrophilic spacer. This structure provides many excellent emulsification and dispersion properties. Composed of naturally derived fatty acids and peptides, it also aids in hair penetration and adhesion. It also aids in skin penetration and damage repair.
